A simple god mode plugin that also watches for people in a Mob Arena
Simply drop the .jar file into your plugins folder.
Provide people the permission MobArenaGod.toggle
Use the command "/mag" to turn god mode on and off
Provide people the permission MobArenaGod.status
use the command "/mag status" to check your current god mode status

There is now a config file, to help with persisting God Mode
This will keep you God Mode enabled across restarts, relogs, and reloads.